  s02: {
    handle: "custom-boonberry/02"
    type: "custom-boonberry"
    payload: "<>"
    excerpt: "\"The Fool was here,\" the grove seemed to say, though no voice spoke it directly. The boonberries reflected strange patterns, hinting at the Fool’s games."
