    handle: "section/05"
    type: "section"
    payload: "{}"
    title: "The Echoes of the Grove"
    excerpt: "In the grove, time did not pass in a linear fashion. Boof felt as if they had already walked this path—yet it was new. The boonberries glowed brighter, as if the Fool's presence had just passed."
